糧提款換美金<br />\n10. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n11. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n12. 盡情杯葛犬二代/狗親屬<br />\n13. Tag或吹你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n<br />\n諗到再加，如果你咁都做唔到，講咩野好忟好惱無野可做。<br />\n只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"7aa32b774310f615b905bdcbe9cd79729df0b872","tid":1532294,"uid":255509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"733fff2d14d4f39fd24d59e9faa24d4c3ca4687b","tid":1532294,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc8a377500744bae044f0cc7c64bdd4d8d3a6700","tid":1532294,"uid":255509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tffv7zw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTffv7zw.jpg&h=5dc0ec06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n要人呀！！<br />\n唔夠人呀<br />\n大家快出<br />\n831 黑警父債子還"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:24:59.000Z","msg":"依家唔同6,7月啦<br />\n<br />\n會勁拉<br />\n唉<br />\n小心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:25:37.000Z","msg":"就係小人先易出事<br />\n需要大量街坊"},{"pid":"2bc6819ffd0be91389efe227f218050d74d5deb8","tid":1532294,"uid":255509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"17/20"},{"pid":"4a43aec0367f17b45af65119a69634bcc1fa5b6b","tid":1532294,"uid":231594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:26:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0efa48933f4d0832dfc49529eff36a6d69ff77ca","tid":1532294,"uid":202846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:26:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27b25ca116ff88250e3660e0845b1e2e382ae186","tid":1532294,"uid":255509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:26:40.000Z","msg":"18/20"},{"pid":"41041d065e4fd2aed182835d157f1a854cc111c3","tid":1532294,"uid":234954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:26:48.000Z","msg":"到！"},{"pid":"6256788148747bb8bf3687fbf9fca31c583eccb0","tid":1532294,"uid":255509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:26:50.000Z","msg